\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces TRIAGE cascade pipeline. All flows enter Stage~1~(\textbf  {SENTRY}), a 50K-parameter neural binary gate. Flows cleared as Benign exit immediately~(No branch); Attack-flagged flows proceed to Stage~2~(\textbf  {XGBoost}) for fine-grained attack-type labelling~(Yes branch). The embedding head and hybrid $\mathcal  {L}_{\mathrm  {BCE}}$\,+\,$\mathcal  {L}_{\mathrm  {SupCon}}$ objective are training-time internals of SENTRY; solid arrows show the inference-time data flow.}}{3}{}\protected@file@percent }
